        "subject": "LU-149 tests: enable async journal commit",
        "message": "LU-149 tests: enable async journal commit\n\nCurrently, the async journal commit feature (bug 19128) and\nthe cancel lock before replay feature (bug 16774) are disabled\nby default on b1_8 branch.\n\nThis patch is to enable them by default so as to trigger\nJenkins build and autotest regression test run.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly \\\nenvdefinitions=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes \\\nclientdistro=el6 serverdistro=el5 clientarch=x86_64 \\\nserverarch=x86_64 testgroup=full\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ib88511a086d3dececfa98bb31589d0eede286eaa\n"
